%h1 Listing services

%p These are all the services you are running. Click on one to view its details, add releases etc. or jump right into one of the actions to the right.

%table
  %tr
    %th Name
    %th Type

  - @services.each do |service|
    %tr
      %td= link_to service.name, service_path(service.id)
      %td=h service.service_type.name
      %td= link_to 'Edit', edit_service_path(service.id)
      %td= link_to 'Remove', service_path(service.id), :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete

%p= link_to 'New service', new_service_path
- content_for :sidebar do
  %h2 Actions
  %ul
    %li= link_to "Add a service", new_service_path